sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant MessagesUI as Messages Dashboard + MessageList
    participant MsgAPI as /api/messages endpoints
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (Prisma)

    Admin->>MessagesUI: Open /dashboard/messages
    MessagesUI->>MsgAPI: GET /api/messages?page=1&status=all
    MsgAPI->>DB: Query messages with pagination
    DB-->>MsgAPI: Message rows
    MsgAPI-->>MessagesUI: List payload
    MessagesUI-->>Admin: Render inbox cards

    Admin->>MessagesUI: Filter by new/read and search
    MessagesUI->>MsgAPI: GET /api/messages?q=&status=new
    MsgAPI->>DB: Query filtered rows
    DB-->>MsgAPI: Filtered messages
    MsgAPI-->>MessagesUI: Updated list

    Admin->>MessagesUI: Mark message as read
    MessagesUI->>MsgAPI: PATCH /api/messages/:id { isRead: true }
    MsgAPI->>DB: Update message status
    DB-->>MsgAPI: Updated row
    MsgAPI-->>MessagesUI: Success
